 player + chat (viewer)\n   - `/login`, `/register` — auth\n   - `/admin` — dashboard (stream status, viewer count)\n   - `/admin/settings` — stream title, description, stream key\n   - `/admin/users` — user list, ban/unban\n   - `/admin/chat` — chat history by session\n\n4. **Tech within Next.js** — App Router, Tailwind, minimal dependencies?\n\nWhat's your thinking on these? Especially — do you want both viewer + admin in one app, or admin-only for now?",
